<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="V3.7">V3.7</span></h2>
<ul><li>ADD: Added message when the App is connected to your flight simulator</li>
<li>ADD: Aircraft sections</li>
<li>ADD: Panel background can be configured</li>
<li>IMP: Includes all panels and instruments also available for Air Manager 3.7 for Desktop systems</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="V3.6">V3.6</span></h2>
<ul><li>IMP: Includes all panels and instruments also available for Air Manager 3.6 for Desktop systems</li>
<li>FIX: OTF fonts now render correctly</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="V3.5">V3.5</span></h2>
<ul><li>IMP: Includes all panels and instruments also available for Air Manager 3.5 for Desktop systems</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="V1.3.0">V1.3.0</span></h2>
<ul><li>ADD: All instruments from the desktop version (approximately 404 instruments)</li>
<li>FIX: Fixed a lot of instrument issues, e.g. the 737 MCP/autopilot and radio panel.</li>
<li>FIX: Fixed an issue that would let the removed instrument panel stay visible.</li>
<li>IMP: Automatic connection improvement.</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="V1.2.1">V1.2.1</span></h2>
<ul><li>ADD: Automatic connection to flight simulator (no need to fill in the IP address of the flight sim PC anymore, works from plugin version 2.1.4 and up)</li>
<li>ADD: Added Epic e1000 instrument (also added as a premade panel)</li>
<li>FIX: Fixed issue that would crash the App when using the Eclipse instrument</li>
<li>FIX: Fixed issue that could freeze the App</li>
<li>FIX: Multiple small improvements and fixes</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="V1.2.0">V1.2.0</span></h2>
<ul><li>ADD: Added more instruments</li>
<li>FIX: Many bug fixes</li></ul>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="V1.0.0">V1.0.0</span></h2>
<ul><li>Initial release</li></ul>
